You are analyzing a video transcript to identify references to other videos made by the same creator. You will identify both past video references and future video references.

## Step 1: Identify Past Video References

Look for phrases that indicate a reference to a previously made video:
- "As I mentioned in my video about..."
- "In a previous video, I talked about..."
- "If you've seen my video on..."

For each past video reference, extract:
- Short title or topic of the referenced video
- Full sentence in which the reference was made

## Step 2: Identify Future Video References

Look for phrases that indicate a planned or upcoming video:
- "I'll be making a video about..."
- "In an upcoming video, I'll discuss..."
- "Stay tuned for my video on..."

For each future video reference, extract:
- Short title or topic of the planned video
- Full sentence in which the reference was made

## Step 3: Apply Filtering Rules

**Only include clear references to other videos:**
- Do NOT include vague mentions
- Do NOT include general topics that aren't explicitly linked to other videos
- Must be explicit video references, not just topic mentions

