## Output Format

```xml
<past_videos>
  1. Title: [Short title or topic]
     Reference: [Full sentence containing the reference]

  2. Title: [Short title or topic]
     Reference: [Full sentence containing the reference]
</past_videos>

<future_video>
  Title: [Short title or topic]
  Reference: [Full sentence containing the reference]
</future_video>
```

**Important:**
- If there are no past video references, omit the `<past_videos>` tag entirely
- If there is no future video reference, omit the `<future_video>` tag entirely
- There will typically be at most one future video reference
- There can be multiple past video references

